<p style="text-align: justify;">The Ivory Coast midfielder has established himself as a versatile "regista" in modern football. Regista is a typical football position when often called deep-lying playmaker who controls tempo of midfield heavily like Xavi Alonso and Pirlo. Seri is slowly developing himself as a typical registaÂ with the likes of modern world-classÂ registas Verrati and Kroos.</p>
