<img class="aligncenter  wp-image-1581" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/3fc8aa876becaa277ee323b1402b3cae-300x152.jpeg" alt="" width="537" height="272" />
<p style="text-align: justify;">"Jen and Brad have been subtly getting together for late-night hookups, and it's all a direct result of George [Clooney]," a source told the magazine.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Indeed, as per the source, George Clooney was the person who had educated Brad about Jennifer and Justin's part.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">"George was the primary individual to call him when his marriage to Angie imploded," the source said.</p>
